---
title: Chicken Sausage & Broccoli Pasta Skillet with Toasted Garlic Panko & Parmesan
description: Need a quick dinner with minimal cleanup (that doesn’t skimp on flavor)? Say hello to this pasta skillet! It's a one-pan wonder that has anticipated your every weeknight need. Tuscan-spiced chicken sausage, twisty cavatappi, and tender broccoli rice are swirled together in a skillet with a decadent Parmesan cream sauce. To top things off, herby toasted panko adds texture and a touch of heat, while extra Parm delivers pure umami. One pan, one dream!
